restSimpleBinding.body:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:xsd='http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema' xmlns:xsi='http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance' xmlns:soapenv='http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/' xmlns:platformCore='urn:core_2018_1.platform.webservices.netsuite.com' xmlns:tranSales='urn:sales_2018_1.transactions.webservices.netsuite.com' xmlns:platformCommon='urn:common_2018_1.platform.webservices.netsuite.com' xmlns:platformMsgs='urn:messages_2018_1.platform.webservices.netsuite.com'> <soapenv:Header> <tokenPassport> <account>{$account}</account> <consumerKey>{$consumer_key}</consumerKey> <token>{$token_id}</token> <nonce>{util:generate-random-string(20)}</nonce> <timestamp>{round((fn:current-dateTime() - xs:dateTime('1970-01-01T00:00:00-00:00')) div xs:dayTimeDuration('PT1S'))}</timestamp>
<signature algorithm="HMAC-SHA256"> {dsig:hmacSHA256signature( $account||'&'|| $consumer_key||'&'|| $token_id||'&'|| util:generate-random-string(20)||'&'|| round((fn:current-dateTime() - xs:dateTime('1970-01-01T00:00:00-00:00')) div xs:dayTimeDuration('PT1S')), $consumer_secret||'&'||$token_secret )} </signature> </tokenPassport> </soapenv:Header> <soapenv:Body> <search xsi:type='platformMsgs:SearchRequest'> <searchRecord xsi:type='tranSales:TransactionSearchAdvanced'> <criteria xsi:type='tranSales:TransactionSearch'> <basic xsi:type='platformCommon:TransactionSearchBasic'> <tranId operator='is' xsi:type='platformCore:SearchStringField'> <searchValue xsi:type='xsd:string'>{$salesOrder_tranId_search}</searchValue> </tranId> <customFieldList xsi:type='platformCore:SearchCustomFieldList'> <customField scriptId='custcol_sfdc_order_line_id' xsi:type='platformCore:SearchStringCustomField' operator='is'> <searchValue xsi:type='xsd:string'>{$sfdcOrderLineId_search}</searchValue> </customField> </customFieldList> </basic> </criteria> <columns xsi:type="tranSales:TransactionSearchRow"> <basic xsi:type="platformCommon:TransactionSearchRowBasic"> <internalId xsi:type="platformCore:SearchColumnSelectField"> </internalId> <item xsi:type="platformCore:SearchColumnSelectField"> </item> <line xsi:type="platformCore:SearchColumnLongField"> </line> <customFieldList xsi:type="platformCore:SearchColumnCustomFieldList"> <customField scriptId="custcol_sfdc_order_line_id" xsi:type="platformCore:SearchColumnStringCustomField"></customField> <customField scriptId="custcol_expiry_date" xsi:type="platformCore:SearchColumnDateCustomField"></customField> </customFieldList> </basic> </columns> </searchRecord> </search> </soapenv:Body> </soapenv:Envelope>

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:platformCommon="urn:common_2018_1.platform.webservices.netsuite.com" xmlns:platformCore="urn:core_2018_1.platform.webservices.netsuite.com" xmlns:platformMsgs="urn:messages_2018_1.platform.webservices.netsuite.com" xmlns:tranSales="urn:sales_2018_1.transactions.webservices.netsuite.com" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"> <soap:Header> <platformMsgs:preferences> <platformMsgs:warningAsError>false</platformMsgs:warningAsError> <platformMsgs:disableMandatoryCustomFieldValidation>true</platformMsgs:disableMandatoryCustomFieldValidation> <platformMsgs:disableSystemNotesForCustomFields>false</platformMsgs:disableSystemNotesForCustomFields> <platformMsgs:ignoreReadOnlyFields>true</platformMsgs:ignoreReadOnlyFields> </platformMsgs:preferences> <tokenPassport> <account>{$account}</account> <consumerKey>{$consumer_key}</consumerKey> <token>{$token_id}</token> <nonce>{util:generate-random-string(20)}</nonce> <timestamp>{round((fn:current-dateTime() - xs:dateTime('1970-01-01T00:00:00-00:00')) div xs:dayTimeDuration('PT1S'))}</timestamp>
<signature algorithm="HMAC-SHA256"> {dsig:hmacSHA256signature( $account||'&'|| $consumer_key||'&'|| $token_id||'&'|| util:generate-random-string(20)||'&'|| round((fn:current-dateTime() - xs:dateTime('1970-01-01T00:00:00-00:00')) div xs:dayTimeDuration('PT1S')), $consumer_secret||'&'||$token_secret )} </signature> </tokenPassport> </soap:Header> <soap:Body> <platformMsgs:update> <platformMsgs:record xsi:type="tranSales:SalesOrder" internalId="{$SalesOrder_internalId}"> <tranSales:itemList replaceAll="false"> { for $i at $pos in ($SalesOrder/itemList/item) return <tranSales:item> <tranSales:item internalId="{$i/internalId/text()}"/> <tranSales:line>{$i/line/text()}</tranSales:line> <tranSales:customFieldList> { if(exists($i/custcol_expiry_date/text())) then <platformCore:customField scriptId="custcol_expiry_date" xsi:type="platformCore:DateCustomFieldRef"> <platformCore:value>{$i/custcol_expiry_date/text()}</platformCore:value> </platformCore:customField> else() } { if(exists($i/custcol_expirydate_lastupdate/text())) then <platformCore:customField scriptId="custcol_expirydate_lastupdate" xsi:type="platformCore:DateCustomFieldRef"> <platformCore:value>{$i/custcol_expirydate_lastupdate/text()}</platformCore:value> </platformCore:customField> else() } </tranSales:customFieldList> </tranSales:item> } </tranSales:itemList> <tranSales:customFieldList xmlns:platformCore="urn:core_2018_1.platform.webservices.netsuite.com"> <platformCore:customField scriptId="custbody_ps_extension" xsi:type="platformCore:StringCustomFieldRef"> <platformCore:value>T</platformCore:value> </platformCore:customField> </tranSales:customFieldList> </platformMsgs:record> </platformMsgs:update> </soap:Body> </soap:Envelope>
